{"type":"question","id":3716,"title":"怎样评价习近平今次的海上阅兵举动？","uid":15,"topics":[1831,136],"contents":"习近平每次阅兵花多少钱？中共拒绝公开。中共《中国日报》唯一一次公开了1999年阅兵耗费30亿人民币。2015年习近平大阅兵媒体普遍报道开销215亿。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D42ikxaW4AAIO4A?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D42ikxaW4AAIO4A?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D42ikxaW4AAIO4A?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n习近平阅兵上瘾。今天在青岛举行的海军阅兵只有习近平登舰看到军舰，其他人在岸上只看到浓雾。习近平上台已是第四次大阅兵了，今年国庆还有第五次大阅兵。每次阅兵耗费100亿人民币以上。这种阅兵节奏只有冷战时苏联元首有过。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D419UY3XoAA82CM?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D419UY3XoAA82CM?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D419UY3XoAA82CM?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D419UY5X4AAxhHA?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D419UY5X4AAxhHA?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D419UY5X4AAxhHA?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-04-23","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}